ample Traps）<br>　野外（Wilderness）<br>　都市冒险（Urban Adventures）<br>　天候（Weather）<br>　位面（The Planes）<br>　环境规则（Environmental Rules）</a><br><br><strong>第十四章：创造NPC（Creating NPCs）</strong><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28148.0" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">NPC职业</a><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=66158.msg613499#msg613499" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">创造NPC（Creating NPCs）</a><br><br><strong>第十五章：魔法物品（Magic Items）</strong><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28645.msg222654#msg222654" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">使用魔法物品（Using Magic Items）</a><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28645.msg222656#msg222656" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">身上的魔法物品（Magic Items on the Body）</a><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28645.msg222656#msg222656" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">破坏和修理魔法物品（Damaging &amp; Repairing Magic Items）</a><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28645.msg222659#msg222659" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">购买魔法物品（Purchasing Magic Items）</a><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28645.msg222660#msg222660" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">魔法物品描述（Magic Item Descriptions）</a><br>　护甲（Armor）<br>　武器（Weapons）<br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=70717.msg663636#msg663636" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">药剂（Potions）</a><br>　戒指（Rings）<br>　法杖（Staves）<br>　权杖（Rods）<br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=70717.msg663636#msg663636" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">卷轴（Scrolls）</a><br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=70717.msg663636#msg663636" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">魔杖（Wands）</a><br>　奇物（Wondrous Items）<br>　智慧物品（Intelligent Items）<br>　诅咒物品（Cursed Items）<br>　遗器（Artifacts）<br>　<a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=28652.0" class="bbc_l